39:20.009 --> 39:22.004
It sort of had this
mirror thing for a face.

39:22.006 --> 39:24.009
I mean, look,
I get it.
I'm no prize, but--

39:24.011 --> 39:25.016
You and me both, brother.

39:25.018 --> 39:27.007
But this thing? Gah!

39:27.009 --> 39:28.011
I mean... Okay.

39:29.022 --> 39:32.007
We're basically
chemistry experiments,
right?

39:32.009 --> 39:35.003
He threw some shit
together in a beaker,
and out popped us.

39:35.005 --> 39:36.015
-Yep.
-We're supposed to be weird.

39:36.017 --> 39:39.014
-Yep.
-He fucked somebody
to get her.

39:39.016 --> 39:41.022
What the fuck
do you have to fuck
to get fucking that?

39:42.000 --> 39:43.019
[Cliff laughing]
I do not know!

39:43.021 --> 39:45.010
Okay, okay.
On the count of three,

39:45.012 --> 39:48.012
we both blurt out what
we think he fucked.

39:48.014 --> 39:49.018
Okay?

39:49.020 --> 39:51.011
One, two--

39:51.013 --> 39:53.006
[Niles] I don't
expect compassion.

39:54.013 --> 39:56.006
How about decency?

39:58.002 --> 39:59.004
You first.

39:59.023 --> 40:01.010
Dorothy's missing.

40:07.001 --> 40:08.001
Dorothy?

40:08.003 --> 40:09.005
[Vic] Dorothy!

40:10.000 --> 40:11.003
Dorothy!

40:12.021 --> 40:14.017
Anything?

40:14.019 --> 40:17.007
[gasps] My God!
What if she fell off
the table?

40:17.009 --> 40:19.005
Oh, no!

40:19.007 --> 40:20.023
What is that? Three feet?

40:21.001 --> 40:23.010
That's two
Empire State Buildings
to a tiny person.

40:23.012 --> 40:25.005
[Cliff] Fuck, fuck,
fuck, fuck!

40:25.007 --> 40:27.001
-[groans] Problem!
-[Vic] What?

40:27.003 --> 40:28.012
[Cliff] She took my cheese.

40:28.014 --> 40:31.007
-[Vic] So?
-So she went to feed
the rats.

40:31.009 --> 40:33.020
She thinks I've been feeding
the fucking rats!

40:33.022 --> 40:34.023
You've been killing
the rats.

40:35.001 --> 40:36.010
[Cliff] No shit!

40:36.012 --> 40:38.007
You think I'm gonna say that
to a little fucking girl?

40:38.009 --> 40:41.000
If she goes anywhere
near that rat hole,
they'll kill her.

40:42.009 --> 40:43.013
Or...

40:44.008 --> 40:45.011
Or what?

40:45.013 --> 40:47.011
She's a very creative
little girl.

40:48.006 --> 40:50.006
Find her!

40:50.008 --> 40:51.017
Rats want war...

40:51.019 --> 40:52.023
it's war!

40:53.001 --> 40:55.010
Jane, you wanna go fuck up
some rats?

40:56.001 --> 40:57.015
Fuck, yes.

40:57.017 --> 40:58.015
I'm in!

40:59.023 --> 41:01.014
-[Cliff] Rita!
-Uh...

41:01.016 --> 41:02.021
[Cliff] Rita's in!

41:02.023 --> 41:04.000
Let's go!

41:18.006 --> 41:19.010
Whoa.

41:21.011 --> 41:23.013
-What the hell?
-[Rita] What's going on?

41:25.019 --> 41:27.011
This is a trap.

41:27.013 --> 41:29.000
This is Mr. Nobody.

41:31.007 --> 41:32.022
Do you see Mr. Nobody?

41:33.000 --> 41:34.005
[Rita] Yes.

41:34.007 --> 41:35.016
[Vic] No.

41:35.018 --> 41:37.002
This is a trap.

41:38.023 --> 41:40.003
This is a trap.

41:40.005 --> 41:41.010
-Victor...
-This is--

41:41.012 --> 41:43.014
Victor!

41:43.016 --> 41:46.016
Mr. Nobody is still
in the painting.

41:46.018 --> 41:48.007
It's not a trap...

41:48.009 --> 41:49.017
and I'm not going anywhere.

41:49.019 --> 41:51.013
-Do you hear me?
-No, this is a trap.

41:55.006 --> 41:56.009
This is a trap.

41:57.023 --> 41:59.001
Dorothy!

41:59.003 --> 42:00.007
Over there.

42:06.001 --> 42:07.008
[Cliff] Dorothy?

42:07.010 --> 42:09.004
Hey, kid. You okay?

42:09.023 --> 42:10.023
Dorothy?

42:11.001 --> 42:12.001
[rats squeaking]

42:12.003 --> 42:13.014
[Cliff] The fuck?

42:13.016 --> 42:14.020
[rats squeaking]

42:18.010 --> 42:19.020
She's a mommy.

42:23.015 --> 42:24.019
[Cliff] Whoa!

42:25.013 --> 42:26.022
There are so many.

42:28.004 --> 42:31.007
[Dorothy] Aw!
What's wrong with
that one?

42:32.017 --> 42:34.000
So small.

42:35.005 --> 42:36.019
What if she doesn't see it?

42:36.021 --> 42:39.003
[Cliff] It's okay.
See? Look.

42:39.005 --> 42:41.015
Mommy rat's picking
it up, and...

42:41.017 --> 42:42.022
[rat screeching]

42:43.000 --> 42:45.004
Oh! Ooh, shit!

42:45.006 --> 42:46.013
[Dorothy]
What's happening?

42:46.015 --> 42:48.012
-[Cliff] Uh...
-What's happening?

42:49.008 --> 42:50.019
Natural order.

42:50.021 --> 42:52.010
-[bones crunching]
-[Dorothy shrieks]

42:52.012 --> 42:55.005
The weakest one is a liability,
so it has to go.

42:55.007 --> 42:56.012
[Dorothy sobbing]

42:56.014 --> 42:58.015
It killed the baby!

43:00.008 --> 43:02.004
[screaming]

43:02.006 --> 43:03.014
[Cliff] Uh, it's okay!
It's okay!

43:03.016 --> 43:04.021
Jane, a little help?

43:04.023 --> 43:06.009
Jane? Jane!

43:06.011 --> 43:08.023
-[Dorothy continues screaming]
-[Cliff] Oh, what the...

43:09.001 --> 43:10.009
[Cliff]
It's okay. It's okay.

43:10.011 --> 43:12.010
Everything is
gonna be okay.

43:12.012 --> 43:14.000
Just fine.

43:14.002 --> 43:15.021
Everything is
gonna be okay.

43:15.023 --> 43:17.002
It's okay. It's okay.

43:17.004 --> 43:18.011
[Niles] Dorothy!

43:18.013 --> 43:19.018
[Cliff] Chief!

43:24.009 --> 43:25.015
What the hell
is going on?

43:25.017 --> 43:26.021
[Cliff] She was just...

43:26.023 --> 43:28.023
This... This rat was, uh...
Babies...

43:29.001 --> 43:31.012
And then, out of nowhere
she just... chop!

43:31.014 --> 43:32.022
I mean, fuck!

43:33.000 --> 43:34.011
[creature growling]

43:35.010 --> 43:37.015
[footsteps thumping]

43:37.017 --> 43:39.007
[creature roars]

43:40.003 --> 43:41.006
No.

43:42.008 --> 43:44.019
Dorothy, listen to me.

43:44.021 --> 43:46.023
Everything is all right.

43:47.001 --> 43:49.003
[shivering] It's not.
It's not.

43:49.005 --> 43:50.018
Please, my love.

43:51.010 --> 43:52.021
Just breathe.

43:52.023 --> 43:54.007
[creature growls softly]

43:55.006 --> 43:56.011
Cliff, don't!

43:56.013 --> 43:59.004
This isn't something
you can just punch.

44:00.018 --> 44:02.014
[creature growls softly]

44:04.001 --> 44:06.018
[Cliff] Hey! Hey, you!

44:06.020 --> 44:08.015
[metal squeaking]

44:08.017 --> 44:10.000
Whoa!

44:13.023 --> 44:15.005
Fuck!

44:15.007 --> 44:17.019
Dorothy, my darling.
I know you're scared.

44:17.021 --> 44:20.001
But you must breathe.

44:20.003 --> 44:21.016
Listen to my voice.

44:21.018 --> 44:23.002
I can't.

44:23.004 --> 44:24.015
-[Cliff] Okay, you wanna go?
-[footsteps thumping]

44:24.017 --> 44:25.018
Let's go!

44:30.017 --> 44:32.007
What the fuck!

44:35.001 --> 44:38.020
Hey, whatever you're
doing to Dorothy,
you better fucking stop!

44:41.009 --> 44:43.005
Okay, weird thing
with the face again.

44:43.007 --> 44:45.018
You wanna dance, too?
Let's do this.

44:45.020 --> 44:47.007
[Niles] Dorothy...

44:47.009 --> 44:50.005
-[creature] <i>Help... girl...</i>
-[Dorothy shudders]

44:50.007 --> 44:53.010
Leave... me... alone!

44:54.014 --> 44:56.004
[loud thudding]

44:56.006 --> 44:58.003
[Cliff] How many imaginary
friends do you have
in there?

44:58.005 --> 44:59.009
Jesus Christ!

44:59.011 --> 45:01.002
-[metallic crash]
-[Cliff screams]

45:01.004 --> 45:04.014
[creature] <i>Make stop.</i>

45:04.016 --> 45:05.023
[Dorothy] He's coming.

45:06.001 --> 45:08.007
-[low growl]
-He's coming!

45:08.009 --> 45:10.012
He won't stop,
he's coming.

45:10.014 --> 45:11.015
You have to!

45:11.017 --> 45:14.002
[creature] <i>Make wish.</i>

45:14.004 --> 45:15.010
[Dorothy] He wants me
to make a wish.

45:15.012 --> 45:16.018
You must keep him back.

45:16.020 --> 45:18.023
-I can't!
-You must!

45:19.001 --> 45:21.009
[creature]
<i>Make wish.</i>

45:22.014 --> 45:25.003
You have to send him back,
you have to!

45:25.005 --> 45:27.004
Don't make me
lock you away again!

45:27.006 --> 45:28.015
[Dorothy gasps]

45:30.008 --> 45:32.005
[roaring stops]

45:36.014 --> 45:38.002
[Dorothy sobbing]

46:17.004 --> 46:18.023
[loud crashing]

46:35.019 --> 46:36.023
[sighs]

46:38.018 --> 46:41.003
[Kipling] I can scarcely
believe it, Caulder.

46:42.022 --> 46:46.010
Cut-throat, scheming,
selfish lone wolf...

46:47.021 --> 46:50.021
giving everything up
for his feckless freaks.

46:50.023 --> 46:53.013
Dorothy needs to
be kept safe.

46:53.015 --> 46:56.015
Away from any situation
that might foster...

46:56.017 --> 46:58.015
Unpleasantness.

46:58.017 --> 47:00.004
And as for the others...

47:02.001 --> 47:03.012
They've suffered enough.

47:05.003 --> 47:07.015
I have to try
and make it right...

47:07.017 --> 47:09.013
in whatever small
way I can.

47:09.015 --> 47:10.020
"Small"?

47:12.007 --> 47:14.004
It's hardly what I call
giving up your life.

47:33.000 --> 47:34.019
<i>Vitae essentia.</i>

47:36.003 --> 47:38.014
No take-backs on
a fool's bargain, Niles.

47:39.015 --> 47:41.010
Only a fool...

47:41.012 --> 47:44.001
would consider himself
before his family.

47:45.008 --> 47:48.005
What lies before me now
is simply...

47:48.007 --> 47:50.000
a riddle I have not yet solved.

47:50.002 --> 47:52.015
[Kipling] Well, you better
solve it quick, old man.

48:11.021 --> 48:13.003
Eat up.

48:13.005 --> 48:14.022
Lot of new mouths to feed.

48:24.001 --> 48:25.002
Ha!

48:29.010 --> 48:30.011
Ha!

48:40.021 --> 48:42.007
[yells]

48:48.016 --> 48:49.019
Vic!

48:49.021 --> 48:51.012
You won't believe it!

49:36.021 --> 49:38.009
Fuck you.

49:38.011 --> 49:39.013
[zipper unzips]

49:40.017 --> 49:42.009
[sighs, sniffles]

50:09.007 --> 50:11.000
[sighs heavily]

50:11.002 --> 50:13.009
[Niles and Dorothy]
<i>Tonight another day</i>
<i>has passed,</i>

50:14.004 --> 50:16.021
and no matter noise,

50:16.023 --> 50:19.009
no matter dark,

50:19.011 --> 50:23.011
we must sit,
and stay,
and wait.

50:24.020 --> 50:26.015
[both whisper]
Or be quiet,

50:26.017 --> 50:29.008
and be polite,

50:29.010 --> 50:32.004
till tomorrow's at the gate.

50:35.018 --> 50:38.001
[sighs]
Good night, my love.

50:41.018 --> 50:43.017
[both chuckle]

50:45.009 --> 50:46.012
[Dorothy sighs]

50:51.020 --> 50:53.010
-Papa?
-Hmm?

50:55.022 --> 50:57.021
You will always
be with me...

50:59.013 --> 51:00.014
won't you?

51:02.007 --> 51:03.023
I'm not going anywhere.

51:12.017 --> 51:14.002
Dream well.

51:26.003 --> 51:27.017
Night-night, Herschel.

51:29.011 --> 51:31.001
You too, Darling.

51:32.013 --> 51:33.015
[giggles]

51:36.009 --> 51:37.016
I love you, too.

51:39.012 --> 51:40.022
Sleep tight.

51:49.019 --> 51:51.003
[creature] <i>Father...</i>

51:52.010 --> 51:53.015
<i>dying.</i>

52:00.019 --> 52:02.020
It's time for bed.

52:04.009 --> 52:06.011
We have to go to sleep.

52:07.003 --> 52:08.015
All of us.

52:09.014 --> 52:11.021
<i>Must... stop.</i>

52:11.023 --> 52:14.007
He's not dying!

52:16.016 --> 52:18.006
You heard him.

52:22.012 --> 52:24.003
He's not going anywhere.

52:24.023 --> 52:27.015
<i>Make... wish.</i>

52:27.017 --> 52:28.022
No!

52:33.015 --> 52:34.018
[sighs]

52:34.020 --> 52:36.008
Not today.

52:42.010 --> 52:43.021
<i>When?</i>

52:46.023 --> 52:48.008
We'll see.
